<div class="story">  <p>Whispering Pines is a mostly wooded subdivision in the heart of Kill Devil Hills with just a little more than 100 properties. Most of the lots are small but the newer lots in the back are large enough to hold a large house and a pool. Backed up to <a href="http://www.nature.org/ourinitiatives/regions/northamerica/unitedstates/northcarolina/placesweprotect/nags-head-woods-ecological-preserve.xml" title="Nags Head Woods">Nags Head Woods</a> on the west side of RT 158, Whispering Pines is located just south of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KillDevilHills/kill-devil-beach.asp" title="Kill Devil Beach">Kill Devil Beach</a> and north of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KillDevilHills/ocean-acres.asp" title="Ocean Acres">Ocean Acres</a>. </p> 
